snippet: The Texas Rangers will add a player with a championship pedigree to their spring training roster on Monday with Super Bowl-champion quarterback Russell Wilson set to join the club in Surprise, Arizona....

headline.print_headline: Super Bowl-Winning QB Wilson to Suit Up for Rangers
headline.main: Super Bowl-Winning QB Wilson to Suit Up for Rangers

lead_paragraph: The Texas Rangers will add a player with a championship pedigree to their spring training roster on Monday with Super Bowl-champion quarterback Russell Wilson set to join the club in Surprise, Arizona.
